## Security Features

This messenger implements the following security measures:

- **E2EE**: Signal Protocol (X3DH + Double Ratchet + PQXDH/ML-KEM-768)
- **Sealed Sender**: hides sender identity from the server
- **Key Transparency**: public audit log of identity keys
- **Canary Token**: detects server compromise
- **Trusted Contacts**: account recovery without server involvement
- **Perfect Forward Secrecy**: session keys rotated per message
- **TLS 1.3**: all traffic encrypted in transit
- **bcrypt**: passwords hashed with cost factor 12
- **JWT**: short-lived access tokens (15 min) + refresh rotation
- **Rate limiting**: Redis sliding window on all auth endpoints
- **Proof-of-Work**: anti-bot protection on registration

